		<div>This is both good and bad.<br />
<br />
It is good in that it shows Sony is listening (sometimes) and that there are issues that need to be fixed before they more onto a new project.<br />
<br />
It is bad in that for people who have been 65 for a while and have done most everything well there is not much new to do.  The increased level cap and the new zones would be a plus to these people.  That and the increased level cap is really needed to help push guild through PoP and on to new content.  How old is PoP and yet the zones still have the most contested content in the game.  As a person who wants to see as much of the game as I can I welcome the chance to get people moving through PoP and on to other things rather than sitting in PoP locking content from smaller guilds.</div>
